### @activities 1 

## Activity 1 @showdialog 
Welcome to the Monitoring Bees and pollination with a bug counter. 

## Step 1 
For this project, we will use the Touch Sensor to detect when a 'bee' has landed on our prototype.  The LED light will turn on when a 'bee' visits the prototype.

